Package: sumvar
Title: Summarise Continuous and Categorical Variables, Check for Duplicates and Missing Data
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Alexander", "Stockdale", , "a.stockdale@liverpool.ac.uk", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: The sumvar package quickly explores continuous and categorical variables. sumvar aims to bring the ease and simplicity of the "sum" and "tab" functions from stata, to R. 
